@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_cwiczg(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (0.93 / ((v2 + 0.44 + v2 + 0.22) + tmp))
    tmp = 0.79
    v1 = (v2 * 0.89)
    v1 = wp.sin(v2)
    v1 = (tmp + wp.exp((v1 + 0.51 - tmp + 0.21)))
    v2 = v1
    v0 = wp.cos((v2 + (tmp + 0.94 - v0 + 0.20)))
    v0 = 0.36
    data[tid] = v0
